# 第二题：[开关灯](https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/T752533?contestId=321591)
## 题目简述
给定$3\times3$的一个01网格，又已知当某个数字变化的时候，上下左右的位置都会变化，例如假设原是
```textplain
A  B  C
D  E  F
G  H  I
```
如果只变化E,会变为
```textplain
 A !B  C
!D !E !F
 G !H  I
```
如果只变化C,会变为
```textplain
A !B  C
D  E !F
G  H  I
```
## 题目分析
只需要把数组开大一点，然后模拟即可
::::success[正确代码]{close}
```cpp
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

const int N = 10;
int a[N][N];
bool now[N][N];

int main()
{
    for(int i = 1; i <= 3; i ++)
    {
        for(int j = 1; j <= 3; j ++)
        {
            cin >> a[i][j];
            now[i][j] = 1;
        }
    }
    for(int i = 1; i <= 3; i ++)
    {
        for(int j = 1; j <= 3; j ++)
        {
            if(a[i][j] % 2 == 1)
            {
                now[i][j] = !now[i][j];
                now[i - 1][j] = !now[i - 1][j];
                now[i][j - 1] = !now[i][j - 1];
                now[i + 1][j] = !now[i + 1][j];
                now[i][j + 1] = !now[i][j + 1];//上下左右中都更改状态
            }
        }
    }
    for(int i = 1; i <= 3; i ++)
    {
        for(int j = 1; j <= 3; j ++)
        {
            cout << now[i][j];
        }
        cout << endl;
    }
}
```
